title: Bug 114470[Smoke]Error message throws when using new Date('3/2/2005') as value in table filter.
description: When using the JavaScript code 'new Date('3/2/2005')' as a value in a table filter, an error message is thrown.
OB: No observed behavior mentioned in the bug report.

SR:
1. Open the report that contains a table filter.
2. Set the filter value to 'new Date('3/2/2005')'.
3. Save the report.
4. Preview the report.
5. Verify that there are no errors displayed on the report page and the table filter works correctly.
